# üé® MASTER IMPLEMENTATION PROMPT: MIRELL√â INSPO GALLERY TRANSFORMATION v1.0

## üìã PROJECT OVERVIEW
Transform Mirell√©'s Inspo section into a premium, Pinterest-style visual discovery platform that achieves **<15% BOUNCE RATE** through exceptional masonry gallery design, strategic content placement (800+ words per page), and advanced schema implementation. This is a **visual-first showcase** with strategically hidden SEO content that ranks for competitive nail design keywords while maintaining a premium, non-text-heavy aesthetic.

**Mission:** Create an overwhelming, premium visual experience that keeps users engaged for 5+ minutes while achieving top rankings for nail design inspiration keywords.

---

## üî¨ RESEARCH-BACKED DESIGN FOUNDATION

### **Visual Discovery Psychology (2025 Standards)**

**1. Masonry Layout Engagement**
- Pinterest's masonry grid drives 47% higher engagement than traditional grids by creating natural scanning patterns
- **Dynamic height variation** reduces visual monotony and encourages 75%+ scroll depth
- **Waterfall effect** creates anticipation ("what's next?") keeping users scrolling
- **Asymmetric balance** feels organic and premium vs rigid grids

**2. Premium Visual Hierarchy**
- Visual aesthetics (simplicity, self-similarity, symmetry, contrast) operate as subliminal factors driving luxury brand engagement
- **Hero Impact:** 70vh minimum for immediate visual immersion
- **Progressive Disclosure:** Content reveals on scroll (never all at once)
- **Image-to-White-Space Ratio:** 60% visuals, 40% breathing room prevents overwhelm
- Clear visuals reduce cognitive load, allowing users to focus on engagement rather than deciphering content

**3. Bounce Rate Reduction Strategy**
- Interactive elements transform static websites into engaging experiences, significantly improving user engagement and reducing bounce rates
- Visual elements aren't just decorative‚Äîthey're essential components of effective communication that can significantly reduce bounce rates
- Interactive elements that boost dwell time combined with conversion-focused design can triple engagement
- **Target Metrics:** <15% bounce rate, 5+ minute dwell time, 75%+ scroll depth

**4. 2025 UX Design Trends**
- Glassmorphism with translucent surfaces and soft shadows creates polished, futuristic look maintaining sleek aesthetic
- Strategic color choices increase CTA clicks by up to 34%
- Microinteractions guide users subtly while adding personality to design
- **Dopamine Design:** Bright, saturated accent colors for interactive elements
- **Kinetic Typography:** Animated text for CTAs

---

## üéØ SEO STRATEGY: HIDDEN POWER

### **Content Placement Philosophy**
**800+ words per page BUT visually hidden/dispersed:**
- **NOT text-heavy pages** - content is strategically placed in:
  - Collapsible "About This Style" accordions (200-250 words)
  - Design Detail modals/overlays (150-200 words per modal)
  - FAQs at bottom (300-400 words total, accordion format)
  - Image alt texts (50-100 words across all images)
  - Meta descriptions & schema (100+ words)

**Visual Result:** User sees 90% images, 10% text - but crawlers see 800+ words of SEO content.

### **Image SEO Strategy (CRITICAL)**

Google extracts information about the subject matter of images from content of the page, including captions and image titles. Images should be placed near relevant text and on pages relevant to image subject matter

**Image Filename Optimization:**
```
Format: [category-slug]-[design-style]-[color/feature]-[number].webp

‚úÖ GOOD Examples:
- french-tips-classic-white-elegant-01.webp
- ombre-nails-purple-pink-gradient-03.webp
- chrome-nails-silver-mirror-finish-05.webp
- seasonal-winter-snowflake-design-02.webp

‚ùå BAD Examples:
- IMG_0234.jpg
- nail-design-1.png
- image.webp
```

**Filename Rules (STRICT):**
1. Lowercase only
2. Hyphens (not underscores)
3. Include 2-3 relevant keywords
4. Descriptive of visual content
5. Unique across entire site
6. 4-7 words maximum
7. No special characters

**Alt Text Formula:**
```
Format: [Long-tail keyword] + [specific visual description] (under 125 chars)

Hero Image:
"[Primary category keyword] inspiration featuring [style details]"
Example: "French tip nail designs inspiration featuring elegant white tips with gold accent variations"

Gallery Images (MUST BE UNIQUE per image):
Image 1: "Classic french manicure with thin white tips perfect for weddings"
Image 2: "Modern french nail art featuring reverse tips in nude tones"
Image 3: "Colored french tips in pastel pink for spring nail inspiration"
Image 4: "Almond shaped nails with gold glitter french tip design"
```

**Alt Text Rules (MANDATORY):**
- ‚úÖ Start directly with description (NO "image of" prefix)
- ‚úÖ Under 125 characters strict
- ‚úÖ Include unique long-tail keyword per image
- ‚úÖ Describe what's actually visible
- ‚úÖ Voice search friendly (conversational)
- ‚úÖ Context-relevant to design category
- ‚ùå Never repeat alt text across images
- ‚ùå No keyword stuffing

**Technical Specs:**
- Hero: 1200x630px, WebP/JPG, <100KB
- Gallery: Variable heights (800-1200px), WebP, <80KB each
- Lazy loading: `loading="lazy"` on all below-fold
- Responsive: Include width/height attributes

ImageGallery schema with associatedMedia array containing ImageObject for each image enables images to appear in Google Image search results and rich snippets

---

## üìê SCHEMA IMPLEMENTATION: COMPREHENSIVE

### **Required Schemas (8 Types - ALL PAGES)**

ImageGallery schema inherits from CollectionPage and MediaGallery, used to represent collections of images with hasPart property for individual ImageObject items

**1. CollectionPage Schema** (Primary)
```json
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "CollectionPage",
  "name": "French Tip Nail Designs - Premium Inspiration Gallery",
  "description": "Curated collection of 40+ french tip nail designs...",
  "url": "https://mirelleinspo.com/inspo/french-tips",
  "image": "https://mirelleinspo.com/images/inspo/french-tips-hero.webp",
  "about": {
    "@type": "Thing",
    "name": "French Tip Nail Art"
  },
  "mainEntity": {
    "@type": "ItemList",
    "numberOfItems": 42,
    "itemListElement": [
      {
        "@type": "ListItem",
        "position": 1,
        "url": "https://mirelleinspo.com/inspo/french-tips/design-1"
      }
      // ... more items
    ]
  }
}
```

**2. ImageGallery Schema** (Nested within CollectionPage)
```json
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "ImageGallery",
  "name": "French Tip Nail Designs Collection",
  "description": "Professional gallery of french tip nail art",
  "associatedMedia": [
    {
      "@type": "ImageObject",
      "contentUrl": "https://cdn.mirelleinspo.com/french-tips-01.webp",
      "caption": "Classic french manicure with thin white tips",
      "thumbnail": "https://cdn.mirelleinspo.com/french-tips-01-thumb.webp",
      "width": "1200",
      "height": "800",
      "encodingFormat": "image/webp"
    }
    // ... 40+ images
  ]
}
```

**3. BreadcrumbList Schema**
```json
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    {
      "@type": "ListItem",
      "position": 1,
      "item": {
        "@id": "https://mirelleinspo.com/",
        "name": "Home"
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "ListItem",
      "position": 2,
      "item": {
        "@id": "https://mirelleinspo.com/inspo",
        "name": "Inspiration Gallery"
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "ListItem",
      "position": 3,
      "item": {
        "@id": "https://mirelleinspo.com/inspo/french-tips",
        "name": "French Tips"
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

**4. FAQPage Schema**
```json
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What nail shapes work best for french tips?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Almond, oval, and square shapes showcase french tips beautifully. Almond and oval elongate fingers, while square provides a classic, clean look. Choose based on your natural nail shape and lifestyle."
      }
    }
    // ... 8-10 questions minimum
  ]
}
```

**5. WebPage Schema**
```json
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebPage",
  "name": "French Tip Nail Designs | Mirell√© Inspiration",
  "description": "Discover 40+ stunning french tip nail designs...",
  "url": "https://mirelleinspo.com/inspo/french-tips",
  "primaryImageOfPage": {
    "@type": "ImageObject",
    "contentUrl": "https://cdn.mirelleinspo.com/french-tips-hero.webp"
  },
  "datePublished": "2025-11-23T08:00:00+00:00",
  "dateModified": "2025-11-23T08:00:00+00:00",
  "isPartOf": {
    "@type": "WebSite",
    "name": "Mirell√©"
  }
}
```

**6. Organization Schema** (Site-Wide)
```json
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Organization",
  "name": "Mirell√©",
  "url": "https://mirelleinspo.com",
  "logo": "https://mirelleinspo.com/logo.png",
  "sameAs": [
    "https://www.pinterest.com/mirelle",
    "https://www.instagram.com/mirelle",
    "https://twitter.com/mirelle"
  ]
}
```

**7. Article Schema** (For Category Pages)
```json
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Article",
  "headline": "French Tip Nail Designs: Complete Inspiration Guide",
  "image": "https://cdn.mirelleinspo.com/french-tips-hero.webp",
  "author": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "Mirell√© Team"
  },
  "publisher": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "Mirell√©",
    "logo": {
      "@type": "ImageObject",
      "url": "https://mirelleinspo.com/logo.png"
    }
  },
  "datePublished": "2025-11-23T08:00:00+00:00",
  "dateModified": "2025-11-23T08:00:00+00:00",
  "mainEntityOfPage": "https://mirelleinspo.com/inspo/french-tips"
}
```

**8. ItemList Schema** (For Gallery Grid)
```json
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "ItemList",
  "name": "French Tip Designs Collection",
  "numberOfItems": 42,
  "itemListOrder": "Unordered",
  "itemListElement": [
    {
      "@type": "ListItem",
      "position": 1,
      "item": {
        "@type": "ImageObject",
        "name": "Classic White French Tips",
        "contentUrl": "https://cdn.mirelleinspo.com/french-tips-01.webp"
      }
    }
    // ... more items
  ]
}
```

**Schema Rules (CRITICAL):**
- ‚úÖ JSON-LD format ONLY (not Microdata/RDFa)
- ‚úÖ All schemas combined <10KB per page
- ‚úÖ Validate with Google Rich Results Test
- ‚úÖ Update dateModified on content changes
- ‚úÖ Never markup invisible content
- ‚úÖ Link schemas together (mainEntity, isPartOf)

