## üé® DESIGN SYSTEM: PREMIUM AESTHETIC

### **Color Psychology & Palette**

Vibrant, intentional palettes capture attention and reduce bounce rates while strategic color choices increase CTA clicks by up to 34%

**Primary Colors:**
```
Burgundy-600: #8b1f42 - Premium brand color, trust & luxury
Burgundy-700: #cc2d5c - Hover states, emphasis, urgency
Burgundy-50: #fdf2f4 - Soft backgrounds, subtle highlights
Cream-100: #fcfaf5 - Page background, warmth & elegance
Gray-900: #111827 - Primary text, high contrast
Gray-600: #4b5563 - Secondary text, captions
```

**Accent Colors (Dopamine Design):**
```
Pink-500: #ec4899 - Playful, energetic CTAs
Purple-600: #9333ea - Luxury, creativity badges
Blue-500: #3b82f6 - Trust, informational elements
Green-500: #10b981 - Success states, confirmations
Gold-400: #fbbf24 - Premium features, VIP indicators
```

**Glassmorphism Effects:**
```css
.glass-card {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.15);
}

.glass-dark {
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}
```

### **Typography Hierarchy**

```css
/* Headlines */
H1: font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; 
    font-size: 4.5rem; /* 72px */
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;

H2: font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 3rem; /* 48px */
    font-weight: 600;

H3: font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem; /* 24px */
    font-weight: 600;

/* Body */
Body: font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1rem; /* 16px */
      line-height: 1.6;

Small: font-size: 0.875rem; /* 14px */

Caption: font-size: 0.75rem; /* 12px */
         letter-spacing: 0.05em;
```

### **Masonry Layout System**

Native CSS masonry with grid-template-rows: masonry creates gapless Pinterest grids increasing engagement by 30%

**Implementation:**
```css
.gallery-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  grid-template-rows: masonry; /* Native masonry - Firefox/Safari */
  gap: 16px;
  padding: 24px;
}

/* Fallback for browsers without masonry support */
@supports not (grid-template-rows: masonry) {
  .gallery-grid {
    columns: 4;
    column-gap: 16px;
  }
  
  .gallery-item {
    break-inside: avoid;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
}

/* Responsive breakpoints */
@media (max-width: 1280px) {
  .gallery-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(240px, 1fr));
  }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .gallery-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(160px, 1fr));
    gap: 12px;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .gallery-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 8px;
  }
}
```

**Image Aspect Ratios (Variable Heights):**
```
Small: 200-300px height (20% of gallery)
Medium: 300-450px height (60% of gallery)
Large: 450-600px height (20% of gallery)

Mix ratios to create organic waterfall effect
```

### **Interactive Elements**

Interactive elements invite users to participate rather than passively consume content, significantly improving engagement and reducing bounce rates

**1. Image Hover Effects:**
```css
.gallery-item {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  border-radius: 12px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
}

.gallery-item:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
}

.gallery-item img {
  transition: transform 0.5s ease;
}

.gallery-item:hover img {
  transform: scale(1.05);
}

/* Overlay with design details */
.gallery-item-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.8), transparent);
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: flex-end;
  padding: 20px;
}

.gallery-item:hover .gallery-item-overlay {
  opacity: 1;
}

.overlay-tags {
  display: flex;
  gap: 8px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.tag-chip {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  padding: 4px 12px;
  border-radius: 16px;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: white;
  font-weight: 500;
}
```

**2. Like/Save Heart Animation:**
```css
.heart-button {
  position: absolute;
  top: 12px;
  right: 12px;
  width: 40px;
  height: 40px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
  z-index: 10;
}

.heart-button:hover {
  transform: scale(1.1);
  background: rgba(255,255,255,1);
}

.heart-button.liked {
  background: #ec4899;
  animation: heartBeat 0.5s ease;
}

@keyframes heartBeat {
  0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
  25% { transform: scale(1.3); }
  50% { transform: scale(1.1); }
}
```

**3. Filter Chips (Active State):**
```css
.filter-chip {
  padding: 10px 20px;
  border-radius: 24px;
  background: white;
  border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
  font-weight: 500;
}

.filter-chip:hover {
  border-color: #8b1f42;
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.filter-chip.active {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b1f42 0%, #cc2d5c 100%);
  color: white;
  border-color: transparent;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(139,31,66,0.3);
}

.filter-chip.active::after {
  content: "‚úì";
  margin-left: 8px;
}
```

