2. Content Outline Document:
markdown# INSPO SECTION CONTENT OUTLINE

## Main Inspo Hub Page (/inspo)

### Hero Section
- H1: "Nail Design Inspiration Gallery"
- Subheading: "Discover 500+ curated nail art designs..."
- CTA buttons: "Explore Gallery", "Get Weekly Trends"

### Stats Bar
- 500+ Design Ideas
- 25+ Style Categories
- Daily New Updates
- 100k+ Inspired Users

### Category Grid (8-12 categories)
1. French Tips
   - Short description (50 words)
   - Design count: 42
   - Cover image
   
2. Ombre Nails
   - Short description (50 words)
   - Design count: 38
   [... continue for all categories]

